3rd Party Node Modules
-----------------------
nodemon
npm install -g nodemon
npm install nodemon
npm install dotenv
npm install express


nodemon - package: running application/server in dev mode.
	  no need to stop and start server every time.


dotenv  - package: To maintain and read application env variable
	  like port, host, db_local  url, server url, 
	  application JWT Secret keys
	  to read the cofiguration variable values.

path    - to create and maintain folder and file paths.
fs      - read and write text files
http    - to create server
node server.js
nodemon server.js
